# Thus us a corporate website locator. The user enters a domain name and the script will return the corporate website, several is it is not certain or there are multiple domains.
# 1) it will search the domain name in the whois database and return the corporate website
# 2) it will search the domain name in the common crawl and return the corporate website
# 3) it will search the domain name in the wayback machine and return the corporate website
# 4) it will search the domain name in the crt.sh and return the corporate website
# 5) it will search the domain name in the google search and return the corporate website